          • [ - ] KylerWard - member since 27-Jan-15

            @richccfc They play in the same positions and each offer different attributes. Allan has more stamina and tackling ability than Zielinski but Zielinski is more technically skilled. Similarly, Jorginho is faster and has better ball control than Diawara but Diawara is more imposing physically and has the uncanny ability to play in tight spots with quickness. I see both sets as near equals, depending on who's in form in front.
